=============================== prussdrv ===============================

Bela uses libprussdrv (also known as am335x_pru_package) by Texas Instruments.
Source available at https://github.com/beagleboard/am335x_pru_package

Further information at http://elinux.org/Ti_AM33XX_PRUSSv2 

